"24:33:47" : {s: 24, a: 33, w: 47, r: "غفر", t: "غَفُورٌۭ", l: "غَفُور", lc: 91, tl: "ghafūrun", lb: "অত্যন্ত ক্ষমাশীল ",e: "(is) Oft-Forgiving", b: "বড় ক্ষমাশীল", f: 51, rm: "protect, cover over, hide, shield, helmet, forgive, pardon, to ask for protection/forgiveness."},
