"24:35:12" : {s: 24, a: 35, w: 12, r: "زجج", t: "زُجَاجَةٍ", l: "زُجَاجَة", lc: 2, tl: "zujājatin", lb: "কাঁচ",e: "a glass", b: "একটি কাঁ চের আবরণ", f: 1, rm: "to pierce/thrust/spear, a thing pointed, to cast or throw a thing from oneself, become narrow and long, glass, glass vessels, lamp."},
